Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨，九龍艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,請下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，AI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始先來試個避難訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟火災跟核子引擎事故的警報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,叫全員到機庫集合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,警報聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，方位1-5-8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在變溫層底下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然完全探測不到推進的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但正在移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是以相當快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,聽不到螺旋槳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是以高速…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是TOY BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯，就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,總之，那傢伙總算露出尾巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,埋伏等待TOY BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,推力三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,浮上至深度180
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,前進三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,深度180
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,#22 JACK IN THE BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,情報還太少，不好判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是九龍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,總之，先去找武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你有聽說要做避難訓練嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有，大概是突發的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得狀況有點怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,潛艦的前半部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有那群傢伙們所在的機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,魚雷、飛彈發射裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,武器彈藥庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大致上有這些區域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,另一邊的後半部是由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,機房、動力爐、居住區、餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以及這個中央指揮中心所構成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我心愛的Danann聽從我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,將中央的隔牆全都封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,從機庫那邊要打開隔牆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不會有人來這裡救你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這個方法很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,機庫裡有AS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要用單分子切割刀\n在隔牆上開洞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我還想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,AI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,變更潛艦前方的空調系統設定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把氧氣濃度固定在最高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一有火花就會引爆，砰的一聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都會變成灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那群因為醉氧\n而渾身興奮的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大概也想不出那種點子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因為艦長是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,五角大廈的高官\n跟不知哪來的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在談些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是借地方給他們而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想被捲入麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長，探測到我方的核子潛艦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,方位2-3-0，距離500
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴薩狄那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要進行聯絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,巴薩狄那…是賽拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要理他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,您老是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是當海軍能平安退役的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,距抵達定點還有20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好，打開水幕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,打開水幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是我年紀大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我會耳鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正流出高濃度的氧氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,門也打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,聯絡指揮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,艦內的通訊全被切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,得想想辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,得想想辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始仔細聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,共鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Danann認定了九龍是艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以普通的程式\n是無法解除認定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只有直接把Danann搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我金庫的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,從裡面拿出另一把鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出萬能鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,萬能鑰匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然後到Danann的心臟地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,第三甲板中央電腦室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到“聖母教堂”去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到那裡再做一次共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，聖母教堂是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的運動神經很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只能靠你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我辦不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有點可疑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你後面的手裡拿著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小要，快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你這死丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是槍聲…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,從指揮中心傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你蠻厲害的嘛，小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,確認事項就是這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,TOY BOX現在在哪附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂您說的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有一艘\n擁有怪物般性能的潛艦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事我們已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我深感惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不過關於詳細內容我也沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你最好記住這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟誰才是世界員警
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,地球主義的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不總是被人稱為是紙上談兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你的祖國一旦瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這理論多少就會帶點真實性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要上去艦橋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種狹小的房間裡\n還真是悶得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,前艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在很火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我還不會殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,取而代之的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到了這種懲罰方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,AI，浮上至潛望鏡的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,速度5海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用ESM搜尋附近的水面艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯，很快就會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我方的核子潛艦\n似乎在追逐著什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,無法取得聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,追逐什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，無法確認該目標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,無法確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,潛艦的艦長是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是賽拉中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,愛獨佔功勞的賽拉是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那傢伙\n這麼起勁追逐的目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在這之後的CIC數據\n隨時拿來給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,TOY BOX似乎被我們的\n核子潛艦抓到尾巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,希望不要發生什麼事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,走掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這件衣服很貴的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在方位3-2-3探測到水面艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,認定為ECHO-1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,美國海軍神盾艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,估測距離為70海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼準備發射魚叉飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一號，二號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,目標ECHO-1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,發射模式BOL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他們無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,目標ECHO-1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,資料登錄完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟發射管口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，一號二號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去聖母教堂才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可是到底在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長，有高熱源物體接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,兩枚魚叉飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎鎖定了本艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,方位1-3-2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,距離8000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？緊急回避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,散佈干擾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長，探測到被魚叉飛彈\n擊中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,左舷2-5-2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,距離2000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我方的神盾艦似乎被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡的TOY BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,潛行至深度250
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,MK48魚雷，三號四號準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒被擊沉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,目標雖無法繼續航行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但依然維持漂浮能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你把彈頭拆下來了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,身為艦長，這是理所當然的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是前艦長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,空包彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,報告狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,左舷甲板及機庫損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,艦載直升機全毀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正進行滅火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,推測爆炸是因為\n直升機的誘爆而產生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,假設這艘TOY BOX潛艦真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很難想像他們會\n無緣無故攻擊美國海軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們明明受到了攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可是那卻是空包彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為這背後有著重要的涵義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對方如果是認真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在應該早已成為灰燼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不知為何\n竟然沒有第二波攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,您不覺得很不自然嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長，暴風雨正在接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,餐廳那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的女朋友好像在餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不過，我不會讓你去那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，關那個混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,馬卡蘭不太可能會背叛我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在餐廳的是新人達尼剛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那個狗屎混帳交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你製造機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想辦法沖過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有討論的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小要很危險，你過去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好跟她道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有哪裡痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我不是拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就算只有我一個人也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才我也一點都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是什麼拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫了我好幾次忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒有你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我早在很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有你在，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要說什麼\n自己一個人也不要緊的這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了，我就暫時…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是攻擊聲納的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再讓你恣意妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,核融合爐是我的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,兩對潛舵是我的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\n「巨人的領域」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，剩下的就靠你了
